{"tid":892194,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地去salon染頭髮會點表達想染咩色？","createTime":"2018-11-06T16:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T05:51:32.000Z","uid":26215,"like":134,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"501b5bae28e4153ca8dfa660a766f7522001589a","tid":892194,"uid":26215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"其實我做洗頭既  唔係髮型師<br />\n<br />\n咁今日我就幫個閪女人客染完個頭<br />\n幫佢吹乾緊既時候佢就已緊閪口閪面咁問我...<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唉...又話幫我染奶茶色 都唔係果樣野黎既<br />\n<br />\n咁佢講完之後我其實又覺得冇咩問題 但係我又係新人 咁就即刻上網搵下奶茶色係點先答穩陣D<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdmTm0L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdmTm0L.png&h=66cbf58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我對一對佢個頭 原全一樣wo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :（指住佢個頭）呢隻咪奶茶色囉 <br />\n<br />\n咁正當我想比我搵果張奶茶比佢睇既時候<br />\n佢同時間又比左佢部手機我睇 <br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vy8a8Hm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVy8a8Hm.png&h=1c74953a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我地大家互望大家既手機大概3秒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：........<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：.........<br />\n<br />\n髮型師就係呢個時候黎接手左 <br />\n然後條女就嬲爆爆咁一粒聲都冇出直至埋單走人...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死港女淨係識飲埋D珍珠奶茶 抵死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 髮型師唔夠國際化 開錯顏色"},{"pid":"8f81e5d465c68e85adbae9676ec852208fb540d7","tid":892194,"uid":106326,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"On9仔有色板睇"},{"pid":"807e91deea4302b2f5389a290e575ed01b67a669","tid":892194,"uid":26215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f81e5d465c68e85adbae9676ec852208fb540d7","tid":892194,"uid":106326,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"On9仔有色板睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"之後我都問番個髮型師做咩唔比佢睇色板<br />\n<br />\n佢話條女睇完都揀唔到 早知要奶茶色 你（髮型師）話事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb9730dc6d6baea76cacc318f181f4a4849728f","tid":892194,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"807e91deea4302b2f5389a290e575ed01b67a669","tid":892194,"uid":26215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f81e5d465c68e85adbae9676ec852208fb540d7","tid":892194,"uid":106326,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"On9仔有色板睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"之後我都問番個髮型師做咩唔比佢睇色板<br />\n<br />\n佢話條女睇完都揀唔到 早知要奶茶色 你（髮型師）話事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"佢要珍珠奶茶色都唔洗染了<br />\n漂完就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71daf89879af7e93d454602bbe4349e282f1af06","tid":892194,"uid":34993,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T19:29:45.000Z","msg":"買杯珍珠奶茶車落個頭到<br />\n奶啦!"},{"pid":"937585e6048621424a0e841fdf528905999ef5b7","tid":892194,"uid":211060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T20:07:33.000Z","msg":"我會話，想染個綠到發光既"},{"pid":"00064960dc3ddd11592a2203865495ffab389d8e","tid":892194,"uid":189336,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T21:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e41c427bb7570a9212fe29530793668cfce266e","tid":892194,"uid":146435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"00064960dc3ddd11592a2203865495f